### TITLE ###
Can write underscored numbers
### INPUT ###
print(1_234)
print(0.123_456)
print(12_34.56_78)
### STDOUT ###
1234
0.123456
1234.5678

### TITLE ###
Can use underscores in args
### INPUT ###
args:
  a int = 1_234
  b float = 0.123_456

  a range [1_000, 2_000]

print(a, b)
### STDOUT ###
1234 0.123456

### TITLE ###
Can use underscores in args range validation
### INPUT ###
args:
  a int = 1_234
  b float = 0.123_456

  a range [1_000, 2_000]

print(a, b)
### ARGS ###
3000
